      "content": "You are right to be cynical about the \"just keep working\" narrative, and the scale of the crisis is indeed overwhelming. However, acknowledging the darkness isn't the same as accepting that it's already over; the reality is that the situation is so dire precisely because we still have the power to change it. Hope isn't about ignoring the doom, but about finding the small, defiant sparks of resilience that refuse to let the world end quietly.",
